## 10. Student Journey: Sign Up to Mentorship

The product journey is optimized to ensure that the student is set up with an actionable, personalized path in under 5 minutes.

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Signup : Student enters Email & Password
    Signup --> AI_Chat : Conversational Profiling (4 questions)
    AI_Chat --> Path_Classified : Target Path chosen by AI Engine
    Path_Classified --> Adaptive_Assessment : Launch 10-Question Skill Test
    Adaptive_Assessment --> Scoring_Calculated : Scoring Formula runs (Normalized 1-10)
    Scoring_Calculated --> Roadmap_Generated : Custom Roadmap built dynamically
    Roadmap_Generated --> Dashboard_Active : Student enters interactive dashboard
    Dashboard_Active --> Mentor_Matched : Mentor recommendation highlights skill gaps
    Mentor_Matched --> Session_Booked : Student schedules 1:1 mentor sync
```

### Visual & Interactive Micro-cues:
- **Gamified Progress Bar**: Keeps the user engaged during the 10-question assessment ("Question 3 of 10").
- **Dynamic Skill Chart**: When the student finishes the assessment, a dynamic radial chart animates in, mapping their strengths and gaps visually.
- **The "Generate" Reveal**: Once the assessment finishes, an animated loader says: *"Curating resources from MIT, freeCodeCamp, and Neetcode based on your target path... Done!"* to establish trust and premium product quality.

